#CircuitBreakerSG D-51

I rarely cook 3-dish meal for lunch, guess today is an exception.

We're having 🍗 Kungbao Chicken Thigh, 🥬 Baby Kai Lan & 🍳 Sunny side up over steamed 🍚 Rice. The yolk seems like it's gonna burst anytime 🙈

Happy mid-week!

Haha ya I want to poke the yolk, so inviting!!!!! 🤗😋😍
@fatdoughsg So worried it will slip off the rice & burst before I snap a pic 😆
Yummy lunch. I love how you are pairing each dish together. 😋
@angeluvfood Thanks dear. Usually can only manage simple 1-dish for lunch 😅
Delish lunch meal 😍 should make more often 😋
@foodie_homechef You bring lunch box to work? Gotta wake up early to prepare?
@yvonnemsw  not really .. ahaha but this  strange period.. sometime yes. Now start to have more makan places offer dine-in .. pheww.
Wow🤤🤤.. this could ideal for my working weekday’s bento lunch box.. 😍🤗
Looks so delish and yet healthy
